			<li id="helpTxt3">Click on the "Sun" icon to view an image clue about the immortal.</li>
			<li id="helpTxt4">Click on the "Zoom" icon to view a larger image of the statue. Once there, click on the "Up" or "Down" arrows or scroll with your mouse to move the image up and down.</li>
			<li id="helpTxt5">When you are done placing the three names, click the "Finished" button. If one or more of your matches are incorrect, the names will return to the left side.</li>
			<li id="helpTxt6">Click on the "Reset" button to return the names to the left side.</li>
			<li id="helpTxt7">To return to the activity, click on the "Close" button.</li>
		</ul>
