				These three immortals appear alike, but look closely for symbols that are clues to their identities. Click the magnifying glass next to each and see if you can find the clues. 
				<p>The names of the three are below. Click on the question mark next to their names to learn something about their stories.</p>
				<p>Then try dragging the name of each immortal to the sculpture that represents her. For another clue, click on the sunburst.</p>
				<p class="errorMsg">Oops, one or more of your matches was incorrect. Please try again.</p>
			</li>
